<p><span>2015</span><span>年至</span><span>2018</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>30</span><span>日，蓝天燃气应收账款账面余额分别为</span><span>2699.91</span><span>万元、</span><span>2874.78</span><span>万元、</span><span>1249.54</span><span>万元和</span><span>1368.19</span><span>万元，占当年营业收入的比例分别为</span><span>1.31%</span><span>、</span><span>1.45%</span><span>、</span><span>0.50%</span><span>和</span><span>0.88%</span><span>，占比较低。</span></p>
